Package com.ibm.avatar.api.exceptions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CircularIncludeDependencyException
    Notifies the user about circular dependencies that arose via include statements.
    FunctionNotInCatalogException
    Exception to throw when a given function is not found in the AQL catalog.
    SchemaParseException
    Exception to cover problems parsing a TupleSchema that has been encoded as a string inside an AOG file.
    TableFunctionNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a table function referenced in a FROM clause cannot be found in the catalog.
    TableFunctionWrongTypeException
    Exception thrown when a table function is declared with an implementing class that is not a subclass of TableUDFBase.
    UnionCompatibilityException
    Exception thrown when two inputs to a UNION ALL stmt are not union-compatible.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TextAnalyticsException.ExceptionType
    Type of exception indicating where the exception occurred, along with an associated text string for printing.

    Wrapper for a list of compiler errors encountered during AQL compilation.
